title: Ruby Rose dons camouflage jacket for Today Show in NY | Daily Mail Online
text: Share 111 shares Ruby's raven locks were slicked down in a side part and was seen sporting a base of make-up. Covering her eyes with round black Vera Wang sunglasses, the actress beamed as she greeted waiting fans as well as photographers. The starlet appeared happy to sign autographs as she made her way into the iconic building in Rockefeller plaza. Combat boots: The action star added platform combat-style heel boots and kept her accessories minimal Clashing prints: The 30-year-old paired the clashing prints with black skinny jeans featuring rips across the thigh and knees Making her way in: Covering her eyes with round black Vera Wang sunglasses the actress beamed as she greeted waiting fans as well as photographers Carrying her phone in hand as she made her way into the NBC studios, the Australian-born beauty appeared to have a backpack on her shoulders. Adding to her US and UK Cosmopolitan covers, the xXX: Return Of Xander Cage star appears on the front of Australia's Cosmopolitan magazine for March, in their gay pride special issue. Ruby recently rekindled her relationship with The Veronica's star Jessica Origliasso. Star signature: The starlet appeared happy to sign autographs as she made her way into the iconic building in Rockefeller plaza The singer shared a snap of the couple's dog sitting next to one of Ruby's magazine covers while the starlet was out of the house. Jessica captioned the sweet shot, in part: 'Ruby Rose, I think we all miss you'. The Orange Is The New Black star is also set to show off her comedy chops soon, currently filming a role in musical comedy Pitch Perfect 3, alongside Rebel Wilson.
